ETHICAL USE CLAUSE

This software is designed for child safety research, education, and authorized
security testing purposes only. Users must:

1. Comply with all applicable laws and regulations
2. Obtain appropriate authorization before deployment
3. Implement human oversight for all decisions
4. Respect privacy and data protection requirements
5. Use the system ethically and responsibly
6. Never use for surveillance without proper legal authority
7. Never deploy without appropriate safeguards

Any use that violates these principles is expressly prohibited.
